{"tid":2307590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警證供矛盾 兩港大生脫堵路罪","createTime":"2020-12-01T09:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T09:13:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22f6759487fcb5cbbf9e2ac15ad35cb9ac1d1b57","tid":2307590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/RXO544UCZVEWNE64ZR37N56REE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FRXO544UCZVEWNE64ZR37N56REE%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0oMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=4ed66ee9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FRXO544UCZVEWNE64ZR37N56REE%2F&h=eea3c9a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/RXO544UCZVEWNE64ZR37N56REE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警證供矛盾 兩港大生脫堵路罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qG2SuoukqwjfnXtMueJS84_fj3g=/1593x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y5KQSM7VKVELJDNQXDZSRZ75HM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqG2SuoukqwjfnXtMueJS84_fj3g%3D%2F1593x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY5KQSM7VKVELJDNQXDZSRZ75HM.jpg&h=eaed2421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■事發當日有示威者在薄扶林道以雜物堵路。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月11日「黎明行動」當天多處有堵路，警方在港鐵香港大學站附近拘捕兩名港大女學生，控告在公眾地方造成阻礙。惟審訊時警察證人供詞不一，例如截停被告的時間地點均有出入，兩人逃避追捕卻突然轉身而遭截查，亦有「內在不可能性」；加上無警員能確認被告確實堵路等疑點，裁定被告罪名不成立，可獲賠訟費。<br />\n<br />\n被告盧。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n截查地點及時間不一<br />\n<br />\n辯方昨申請訟費時透露曾要求撤控，但控方拒絕。控方指兩被告明知有人堵路，仍選擇走向黑衣人，是自招嫌疑。裁判官崔美霞不認同，認為黑衣人逃跑之時，兩被告早已身處天橋上。<br />\n<br />\n崔官裁決時指，有警員供稱相距一兩個身位追逐兩被告，兩人轉身然後被截停，惟該警員書面供詞沒提及被告轉身。此外兩人若是堵路者，必知警員追捕，突然轉身有「內在不可能性」。<br />\n<br />\n崔官又指，有警員稱在地面截停李，但女警的會面紀錄則指截停位置是在天橋上的港鐵站A3出口，時間亦不一致。崔官認為時間地點同樣出錯並不常見，有關鍵矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC683/20"},{"pid":"31961e9c09528e8b9f1e30844433381a4f059fe6","tid":2307590,"uid":165136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"鄭姓裁判官：矛盾即係無夾口供，誠實可靠，必需判監禁刑罰"},{"pid":"eaf2273d4b8026ed085a1ce8340180608b002ee0","tid":2307590,"uid":266519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31961e9c09528e8b9f1e30844433381a4f059fe6","tid":2307590,"uid":165136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"鄭姓裁判官：矛盾即係無夾口供，誠實可靠，必需判監禁刑罰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:12:09.000Z","msg":"又係姓鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde1ecc90c41e312bef1eaf94a0d2a3e604f52ce","tid":2307590,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EaTbjg4U4AAYsFR?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEaTbjg4U4AAYsFR%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=471a672f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6b47172a127fdb68adb84c61ee7a0e70bc479d7","tid":2307590,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"崔官真係一時時 不過好似幾睇重程序正義咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見打得甩嘅多數都係程序問題"}]}